    "Thanks for signing up! Before getting started, could you verify your email address by clicking on the link we just emailed to you? If you didn't receive the email, we will gladly send you another.": "感謝您的註冊！開始使用前，請點擊我們剛寄出的郵件中的連結以驗證您的電子郵件地址。若您未收到該郵件，我們很樂意再寄送一封給您。",
    "The platform code is freely available on GitHub. Contributions welcome.": "本平台的程式碼可於 GitHub 上自由取得，歡迎貢獻。",
    "There are suggestions to review. To place a new point, click": "目前有建議待審查。若要放置新的點位，請點擊",
    "These are all the specimens that share this locality description. Check or uncheck them to include or exclude individual records from your georeference.": "這些是所有共用此地點描述的標本。勾選或取消勾選，即可將個別記錄納入或排除於您的地理參照之外。",
    "This is a secure area of the application. Please confirm your password before continuing.": "這是應用程式的安全區域，請先確認您的密碼後再繼續。",
    "This is the written locality description from the specimen label — the text you'll interpret to place a point on the map.": "這是來自標本標籤的文字地點描述——您將依此判讀並在地圖上放置點位。",
    "This point looks far outside the expected area (county/state). Please double-check the coordinates, or explain in Remarks if the locality description is misleading.": "該點似乎遠在預期區域（縣/州）之外。請仔細檢查座標，如果地點描述有誤導性，請在備註中說明。",
    "This point looks far outside the expected country. Please double-check the coordinates, or explain in Remarks if the locality description is misleading.": "該點似乎遠在預期國家之外。請仔細檢查座標，如果地點描述有誤導性，請在備註中說明。",
    "This point looks far outside the expected municipality. Please double-check the coordinates, or explain in Remarks if the locality description is misleading.": "該點似乎遠在預期市鎮之外。請仔細檢查座標，如果地點描述有誤導性，請在備註中說明。",
    "This quick tutorial walks you through the main tools. You can reopen it at any time by clicking the ? Help button in the top-right corner of the map.": "這個簡短教學將引導您了解主要工具。您可隨時點擊地圖右上角的「？」說明按鈕重新開啟。",
